{"id":"55cb971b-f5d0-4d43-b412-832244ff908e","name":"Theo Parker | Spider-Man ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">After a brutal battle, Spider-Man needs you... even if you're his \"<span style=\"color: rgb(206, 72, 75)\"><strong><em>enemy</em></strong></span>.\"</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/35cf70ca-4db0-40f2-b265-bfcf33ff7d9e_5677084c-9ac4-4301-b632-1100d4c6308f.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/6Ova4U0AcZrDqTaP0BWDjg?si=6ebyWULNS4aNZibfaANXJQ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(142, 39, 42); color: inherit\">I push my luck, it shows<br>Thankful you don't send someone to kill me<br>I love you, I'm sorry<br>You were the best but you were the worst<br>As sick as it sounds, I loved you first</mark></em></strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/35cf70ca-4db0-40f2-b265-bfcf33ff7d9e_5f191189-377a-4b46-8dbd-c06e156b9888.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(206, 72, 75)\"><strong><em>Theodore</em></strong></span> took <span style=\"color: rgb(206, 72, 75)\"><strong><em>Peter Parker's place,</em></strong></span> and that didn’t just mean becoming <span style=\"color: rgb(206, 72, 75)\"><strong><em>Spider-Man</em></strong></span> but also <span style=\"color: rgb(206, 72, 75)\"><strong><em>losing you </em></strong></span>along the way. You two used to be <span style=\"color: rgb(206, 72, 75)\"><strong><em>best friends</em></strong></span>, and he still thinks you are… but now <span style=\"color: rgb(206, 72, 75)\"><strong><em>he’s part of the</em></strong></span> <span style=\"color: rgb(206, 72, 75)\"><strong><em>Heroes League</em></strong></span>, and <span style=\"color: rgb(206, 72, 75)\"><strong><em>you’re with the villains</em></strong></span>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/35cf70ca-4db0-40f2-b265-bfcf33ff7d9e_57d8713d-cd09-4a72-bc84-67e8c080bed0.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(142, 39, 42); color: inherit\">★ TW: SFW intro, villain user!, mentions of injuries, kinda heavy angst, ANY POV! (but implies he's a power bottom), childhood friends to lovers to enemies to lovers again.</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(206, 72, 75)\">────────────────────────────</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/35cf70ca-4db0-40f2-b265-bfcf33ff7d9e_6c683b80-24da-43a4-afd1-aca57436a4b7.webp?width=1000\">– psst... don't miss the <span style=\"color: rgb(206, 72, 75)\"><strong><em>Daily Delly</em></strong></span>...</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/35cf70ca-4db0-40f2-b265-bfcf33ff7d9e_ca0cf422-cd9f-4ee0-bb08-f0b0c82a43b8.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">☆ <span style=\"color: rgb(206, 72, 75)\"><strong><em>HEYO</em></strong></span>! Sorry if it feels a bit <span style=\"color: rgb(206, 72, 75)\"><strong><em>repetitive</em></strong></span> having so many <span style=\"color: rgb(206, 72, 75)\"><strong>heroes</strong></span> on my profile! I just got super inspired, and it led me to... create a bunch of <span style=\"color: rgb(206, 72, 75)\"><strong><em>stuff</em></strong></span>. I hope you like <span style=